column9: Week of Training indicates what resources are needed per week of the training, the training can be started in any week
Type is the Type Rating of the instructor needed
Capacity Needed the the number of instructors needed
Simulator Needed is the number of simulators required for that week of training
Max Students is the maximum number of students that can participate in the training, based on the resources used
Capacity Gained is the trainees that are available to fly on that week as part of their training
